**** Spectral Libraries ****

Create a new Spectral Profile field based on a text field called “Reflectance” 
Open the field calculator field calculator icon
Use the spectralMath function to calculate reflectances from the ASD radiances measured from field spectra and its corresponding white reference.

spectralMath("<profile field 1>", ..., "<profile field n>",
'<python code>', '<output format>')
   
spectralMath("Spectrum",  "Reference",
'y = y1 / y2', 'text')
